ent leader transportation hexion “it complements our full range of products for compression molding including resin transfer molding rtm liquid compression molding lcm and prepreg molding” the new epoxy smc product is supplied as an easytohandle resinplushardener system with optional mold release agent customers have ready access to hexion’s comprehensive technical assistance for more information please consult hexion—hall  booth g—during the jec world  international composites event in paris march  or visit hexioncomautomotive or hexioncomcontacts about the company based in columbus ohio hexion inc is a global leader in thermoset resins hexion inc serves the global wood and industrial markets through a broad range of thermoset technologies specialty products and technical support for customers in a diverse range of applications and industries hexion inc is controlled by investment funds affiliated with apollo global management llc additional information about hexion inc and its products is available at wwwhexioncom contacts hexion incinvestors and mediajohn kompa johnkompahexioncom contacts hexion incinvestors and mediajohn kompa johnkompahexioncom search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up hexionmomentive merger made official  compositesworld go ☰ ⌕ hexionmomentive merger made official momentive performance materials has completed acquisition of epoxy manufacturer hexion specialty chemicals creating a new company that will keep the momentive name news post  related suppliers momentive performance materials inc  momentive performance materials holdings inc albany ny the parent company of momentive performance materials inc and hexion llc columbus ohio the parent company of epoxy manufacturer hexion specialty chemicals inc completed a previously announced merger on oct  the resulting firm will retain the momentive name the combination creates a company with  production facilities more than  employees annualized sales of approximately  billion usd and a pro forma adjusted ebitda of  billion headquartered in columbus ohio the new momentive makes approximately  percent of its sales in fastgrowing regions including the bric countries brazil russia india and china with the balance in more mature markets  percent in europe and  percent in north americathe combined company is organized into three global business divisions silicones and quartz led by president steven delarge and headquartered in albany ny epoxy phenolic and coating resins led by president joseph bevilaqua and forest products under president dale plante “our new combined enterprise now can offer a broader portfolio of specialty technologies and products to meet the diverse applications needs of our global customers” says momentive chairman and ceo craig o morrison “these technologies include silicones epoxies quartz phenolics acrylics aminos acids and others that are used alone or in combination across thousands of critical industrial and consumer applications where superior performance is required”momentive performance materials was formed in  through the acquisition of ge advanced materials hexion specialty chemicals was formed in  when the previously independent borden chemical inc resolution performance products inc resolution specialty materials inc and bakelite ag merged into a single entity hexion’s formerly resolution performance product’s epoxy resin systems are wellestablished in the composites industry including epikote and epikure epoxy systems formulated for wind turbine blade fabrication  news sgl carbon se acquires shares from tokai carbon co ltd composite recycling technology center ceo to retire chief operating officer named ceo northern composites looks to expand products and reach n technologies udri partner for highvolume production of nanostitch largeformat d printer builds carbon fiberreinforced submarine zones blog magazine sourcebook products events news webinars site map subscribe contact about cw advertise social media    